Important
=========
    
    To run the script the file framework/ServiceAPI.py is required.


Installation
============
    
0)  Install the scripting layer for android on your device, which can
    be found here:
        
        http://code.google.com/p/android-scripting/
    
    Additionally install the PythonForAndroid package.
    
1)  To run the script copy the files to your android device to the
    following location:
    
    /sdcard/sl4a/scripts/
    
    The script can now be executed using SL4A.
